::: {#4b12ac97 .cell execution_count=19}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# Rule 2: stop when the e-value is at least 20 (= 1 / 0.05).
fit.evalue(
    mixture_precision=mixture_precision,
).loc["treated"]
```

